<div id="review_2395338712" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2395338712" />
    <a title="Hasham Rasool" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/43718887-hasham-rasool"><img alt="Hasham Rasool" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1481063146p2/43718887.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2395338712?book_show_action=true">May 26, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Hasham Rasool" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Hasham Rasool" href="/user/show/43718887-hasham-rasool">Hasham Rasool</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780990387688" href="/book/show/26314701-reclaim-your-heart">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43718887-hasham-rasool?shelf=yasmin-mogahed">yasmin-mogahed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43718887-hasham-rasool?shelf=religion">religion</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43718887-hasham-rasool?shelf=poem">poem</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43718887-hasham-rasool?shelf=favourites">favourites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43718887-hasham-rasool?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/43718887-hasham-rasool?shelf=islam">islam</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2395338712" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5508388784954129702">Many of us live our lives entrapped by the same repeated pattern of heartbreak and disappointment. Often, we have no idea why this happens. Reclaim Your Heart is about freeing the heart from this slavery. It is about the journey in and out of life&apos;s most deceptive traps. <br/><br/>This book was written to awaken the heart and provide a new perspective on love, loss, happiness, and pain. A manual of sorts, Reclaim Your Heart will teach readers how to live in this life without allowing life to own you. It i</span>
  <span id="freeText5508388784954129702" style="display:none">Many of us live our lives entrapped by the same repeated pattern of heartbreak and disappointment. Often, we have no idea why this happens. Reclaim Your Heart is about freeing the heart from this slavery. It is about the journey in and out of life's most deceptive traps. <br /><br />This book was written to awaken the heart and provide a new perspective on love, loss, happiness, and pain. A manual of sorts, Reclaim Your Heart will teach readers how to live in this life without allowing life to own you. It is a manual of how to protect your most prized possession-the heart.<br /><br />Alhamdulillah, I want to thank to Allah for letting me read this book. I truly love this book a lot and I can't live without this book.<br /><br />Sister Yasmin Mogahed's words have hit me so hard. Yasmin Mogaged is one of my favourite writer. <br /><br />I would massively recommend Muslims and non Muslims to read this book. Everyone, this book is a must read!</span>
  <a data-text-id="5508388784954129702" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


